targets.formattedQuery:
WITH final AS (
  SELECT
    run_id,
    toStartOfInterval(requested_at, INTERVAL 5 minute) AS time,
    argMax(status, event_time) AS final_status,
    argMax(latency_ms, event_time) AS latency_ms
  FROM reports.report_runs_v
  WHERE requested_at BETWEEN toDateTime(intDiv(${__from}, 1000), 'UTC')
                        AND toDateTime(intDiv(${__to}, 1000), 'UTC')
  GROUP BY run_id, time
)
SELECT
  time,
  100.0 * countIf(final_status = 'SUCCESS' AND latency_ms <= 10000)
       / nullIf(countIf(final_status IN ('SUCCESS','FAILED')), 0) AS pct_met_10s,
  100.0 * countIf(final_status = 'SUCCESS' AND latency_ms <= 30000)
       / nullIf(countIf(final_status IN ('SUCCESS','FAILED')), 0) AS pct_met_30s
FROM final
GROUP BY time
ORDER BY time

targets.formattedQuery:
/* grafana dashboard='Reporting SLA Observability', user=0 */
WITH final AS (
  SELECT
    run_id,
    argMax(status, event_time)     AS final_status,
    argMax(latency_ms, event_time) AS latency_ms
  FROM reports.report_runs_v
  WHERE requested_at BETWEEN toDateTime(intDiv(1767140977136, 1000), 'UTC')
                        AND toDateTime(intDiv(1767144577136, 1000), 'UTC')
  GROUP BY run_id
),
bucketed AS (
  SELECT
    multiIf(
      final_status = 'FAILED', '>30s',
      latency_ms <= 1000,  '≤1s',
      latency_ms <= 3000,  '≤3s',
      latency_ms <= 10000, '≤10s',
      latency_ms <= 30000, '≤30s',
      '>30s'
    ) AS tier,
    multiIf(
      final_status = 'FAILED', 5,
      latency_ms <= 1000,  1,
      latency_ms <= 3000,  2,
      latency_ms <= 10000, 3,
      latency_ms <= 30000, 4,
      5
    ) AS sort_key
  FROM final
)
SELECT
  tier,
  count() AS runs
FROM bucketed
GROUP BY tier, sort_key
ORDER BY sort_key

WITH final AS (
  SELECT
    run_id,
    argMax(status, event_time) AS final_status,
    argMax(latency_ms, event_time) AS latency_ms
  FROM reports.report_runs_v
  WHERE requested_at BETWEEN toDateTime(intDiv(${__from}, 1000), 'UTC')
                        AND toDateTime(intDiv(${__to}, 1000), 'UTC')
  GROUP BY run_id
)
SELECT
  multiIf(
    final_status = 'FAILED', 'FAILED',
    final_status NOT IN ('SUCCESS','FAILED'), 'IN_FLIGHT',
    latency_ms <= 1000,  '≤1s',
    latency_ms <= 3000,  '≤3s',
    latency_ms <= 10000, '≤10s',
    latency_ms <= 30000, '≤30s',
    '>30s'
  ) AS tier,
  count() AS runs
FROM final
GROUP BY tier
ORDER BY runs DESC

WITH final AS (
  SELECT
    run_id,
    argMax(status, event_time) AS final_status,
    argMax(latency_ms, event_time) AS latency_ms,
    max(requested_at) AS requested_at
  FROM reports.report_runs_v
  WHERE requested_at BETWEEN toDateTime(intDiv(${__from}, 1000), 'UTC')
                        AND toDateTime(intDiv(${__to}, 1000), 'UTC')
  GROUP BY run_id
)
SELECT
  toStartOfMinute(requested_at) AS time,
  countIf(final_status != 'FAILED' AND latency_ms > 30000) AS sla_breaches,
  countIf(final_status = 'FAILED') AS exec_failures
FROM final
GROUP BY time
ORDER BY time

panels.title: Slow Runs Over Time (SLA breaches >30s vs Exec failures)

targets.formattedQuery:
WITH final AS (
  SELECT
    run_id,
    argMax(status, event_time) AS final_status,
    argMax(latency_ms, event_time) AS latency_ms
  FROM reports.report_runs_v
  WHERE requested_at BETWEEN toDateTime(intDiv(${__from}, 1000), 'UTC')
                        AND toDateTime(intDiv(${__to}, 1000), 'UTC')
  GROUP BY run_id
)
SELECT
  multiIf(
    latency_ms <= 1000,  '≤1s',
    latency_ms <= 3000,  '≤3s',
    latency_ms <= 10000, '≤10s',
    latency_ms <= 30000, '≤30s',
    '30s+'
  ) AS bucket,
  count() AS runs
FROM final
WHERE final_status = 'SUCCESS' AND latency_ms IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY bucket
ORDER BY
  multiIf(bucket='≤1s',1,bucket='≤3s',2,bucket='≤10s',3,bucket='≤30s',4,5)
